last night i cried for hours you know?
Mm-hmm, it sounds like you were experiencing a lot of emotion last night. Can you tell me more about what was happening for you? What feelings were coming up?
i was feeling so lonely i felt i had no one to go to

I'm sorry to hear that you felt so lonely. It sounds like your stressed side was really active, feeling isolated and perhaps a bit overwhelmed. Can you sense what your mature side might say to comfort that lonely part of you?
i think it wil try to sympathize  and say i am here for you we are enough for one another .. but there is a fear in me of losing people

That fear of losing people might be coming from your stressed side, which is trying to protect you from past experiences of loss or abandonment. i lost my mother to a disease

It makes sense that your stressed side might carry a fear of losing people, given that experience. How does your mature side respond to this part of you that feels afraid and lonely?
